author: andreasmyth
msg: Lookup of RMAssertion from a WS Policy specified in WSDL.

This is very primitive at the moment (i.e. does not perform policy intersection or anything the like) - just takes the first child of type RMAssertionType of a Policy element that is attached to the endpoint's binding or port element. If a PolicyReference is attached to the binding or port element instead, this reference is resolved provided it is local.
